StartSmall start page replaces your default new tab page with a minimalist set of features to start your browsing comfortably.

With StartSmall, you can choose high quality wallpapers from great photographers around the world. You can apply your own color scheme, or you can generate a color scheme based on your wallpaper. You can also plan your day with our simple and useful calendar and weather widget.
